	<li id="menu-item-102262" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-102262"><a href="https://www.truthdig.com/category/poetry/">Poetry</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li id="menu-item-5469" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-5469"><a href="/td-originals">TD Originals</a>
